OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1779214266
OL,3,CSiam Cup victory for Guernsey men and
OL,4,CJersey women
OL,6,FThe Siam Cup honours were split at
OL,7,FFootes Lane, as Guernsey men reclaimed
OL,8,Ftheir trophy and Jersey women held on
OL,9,Fto theirs.
OL,11,FGuernsey's men won the game 35-28 and
OL,12,FJersey's women held on for their first
OL,13,Faway win with a close 20-19 victory on
OL,14,FSaturday.
OL,16,FIn more Sarnian success, Guernsey took
OL,17,Fhome the Nash Cup but a draw in the
OL,18,FFallaize means Jersey retain the
OL,19,Ftrophy as last years winners.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
