PN,38802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1779214266
OL,3,CSiam Cup victory for Guernsey men and
OL,4,CJersey women
OL,6,FGuernsey women dominated early on with
OL,7,Fa crowd-pleasing early try from Marni
OL,8,FDe Freitas Alves.
OL,10,FOnly for Jersey to come back and
OL,11,Fequalise minutes later with try by
OL,12,FGeorgina Ruellan, with the score at 5-
OL,13,F5.
OL,15,FTwo more tries from Jersey's Laura
OL,16,FTurpin and Emily Duncan put them into
OL,17,Fa comfortable half time lead at 15-5.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
