OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1779214266
OL,3,CSiam Cup victory for Guernsey men and
OL,4,CJersey women
OL,6,FSeren Coombs added a fourth try early
OL,7,Fin the second half and Guernsey were
OL,8,Fbeginning to look like they'd be
OL,9,Fsoundly beaten.
OL,11,FBut they dug deep with Tanya Scholtz
OL,12,Fand Daisy Travers scoring two tries
OL,13,Ffor the greens in quick succession.
OL,15,FThat late rally from Guernsey took the
OL,16,Fscore to 20-17 with minutes to go.
OL,18,FConversion from Tiegan Batiste on the
OL,19,FSarnian side put just a point in it.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
