OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1779214266
OL,3,CSiam Cup victory for Guernsey men and
OL,4,CJersey women
OL,6,FJersey held on to take the game and
OL,7,Fthe Siam Cup 20-19.
OL,9,FSpeaking to ITV Channel after the
OL,10,Fgame, Jersey women's Captain Katie De
OL,11,FLa Cloche said: "I'm a bit lost for
OL,12,Fwords to be honest. That game could
OL,13,Fhave gone either way at any point.
OL,15,F"We didn't make it easy for ourselves.
OL,16,FIt was touch and go until the very end.
OL,18,F"It's the best feeling in the world.
OL,19,FThis has been a long time coming. It's
OL,20,Fbeen 4 years since we won at this,
OL,21,Fit's amazing."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
