OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1779214266
OL,3,CSiam Cup victory for Guernsey men and
OL,4,CJersey women
OL,6,FGuernsey added to their tally after
OL,7,Fthe break with John Dawe and quickly
OL,8,Fconverted which gave them a 23-7 lead.
OL,10,FWith 20 minutes on the clock Anthony
OL,11,FArmstrong took the score to 28-7.
OL,13,FQuickly fighting back, a try for
OL,14,FJersey in response from Dan Barnes
OL,15,Fconverted, 28-14.
OL,17,FEnd to end responses continued as
OL,18,FGuernsey scored again with a penalty
OL,19,Ftry to stretch their lead to 35-14.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1779214266
OL,3,CSiam Cup victory for Guernsey men and
OL,4,CJersey women
OL,6,FA runaway try for Jersey's Fergus
OL,7,FLudlam as he covered the length of the
OL,8,Ffield in the closing stages, which
OL,9,Ftook the score to 35-21 after a
OL,10,Fsuccessful conversion.
OL,12,FThe tries came thick and fast as Jerry
OL,13,FSexton added to the Jersey run of
OL,14,Fscoring.
OL,16,FBut it was 35-28 on the whistle and
OL,17,FGuernsey claimed back the Siam Cup.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
