FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1779214266
OL,3,CSiam Cup victory for Guernsey men and
OL,4,CJersey women
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Channel, Jordan
OL,7,FReynolds, Guernsey's Director of Rugby
OL,8,Fsaid: "These guys don't need form,
OL,9,Fthey need motivation and the Siam
OL,10,Fbrings that.
OL,12,F"I thought our performance today was
OL,13,Fexcellent. I know we leaked a couple
OL,14,Fof late tries but our forward pack
OL,15,Fdominated up front which was great.
OL,17,F"We get to lift the trophy and keep it
OL,18,Fhere for 12 months."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
