PN,38809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1779214266
OL,3,CSiam Cup victory for Guernsey men and
OL,4,CJersey women
OL,6,FJersey's Director of Rugby, Myles
OL,7,FLandick said: "At halftime we went in
OL,8,Fknowing that we were still in the
OL,9,Fgame, Guernsey scored early in the
OL,10,Fsecond half which made it a bit more
OL,11,Fdifficult.
OL,13,F"Had there been that 3 or 4 minutes
OL,14,Flonger then who knows, but at the end
OL,15,Fof the day its been a fantastic battle.
OL,17,F"Footes Lane is really difficult to
OL,18,Fcome away to and history has shown it
OL,19,Ffavours the home side.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1779214266
OL,3,CSiam Cup victory for Guernsey men and
OL,4,CJersey women
OL,6,F"It does push you on, that's the
OL,7,Fbeauty of the challenge coming away
OL,8,Ffrom home. It just wasn't to be for us
OL,9,Ftoday."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/10
